                        Sesuaikan dengan <b>Periodic Inform Interval</b> di CPE Anda (biasanya 15–30 mnt).
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:10px">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="save(['acs_url','acs_user','acs_pass','acs_vparams','acs_path_pppoe','acs_path_ip','acs_online_threshold'])">💾 <%= t.save %></button>
